<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbfdfd05e-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s15115"><num value="15115">§ 15115.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idbfdfd05f-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s15115/a"><num value="a" class="bold">(a)</num><heading class="bold"> Scholarships</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated to carry out <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s15113">section 15113 of this title</ref> $800,000 for fiscal year 2001 and such sums as may be necessary for each of fiscal years 2002 through 2007.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idbfdfd060-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s15115/b"><num value="b" class="bold">(b)</num><heading class="bold"> Staff development curriculum</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated to carry out <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s15114">section 15114 of this title</ref> $800,000 for fiscal year 2001 and such sums as may be necessary for each of fiscal years 2002 and 2003.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
